Whose is this?

165
00:12:49,268 --> 00:12:51,937
But that's Heon's.

166
00:12:53,939 --> 00:12:54,857
Give it to me, sir.

167
00:12:55,733 --> 00:12:57,151
I asked him to lend it to me.

168
00:12:57,735 --> 00:12:58,819
Okay.

169
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:39,318
ON

