00:17:21,415 --> 00:17:23,834
Who in the world did this?

217
00:17:23,917 --> 00:17:25,127
Come out this instant!

218
00:17:25,711 --> 00:17:26,920
Open the door!

219
00:17:27,838 --> 00:17:29,048
Who's in there?

220
00:17:29,131 --> 00:17:31,383
Open up! One, two…

221
00:17:32,051 --> 00:17:34,219
